# The start symbol is START.

# These two rules are required; choose their weights carefully!
99	START	S1
0	START	S2

# This is a very, very, very simple grammar to get you started.

1	S1	NP VP EndOS

1	VP	Verb NP
1	VP	Verb
1	VP	DoDoes

#1	NP	Noun
#20	NP	Det Nbar
#1	NP	ProperGroup

#8	ProperGroup	Proper
#1	ProperGroup	Det Proper


#20	Nbar	Noun
#1	Nbar	Nbar PP

#1	PP	Prep NP

1	Location	Prep Proper



1	S1	Verb Prep Proper Verb Adj EndOS



# Questions

1	S1	Question

1	Question	Interrogation NP PronomVP ?
1	Question	InterInv NP PronomVP ?


1	Interrogation	DoDoes
1	Interrogation	WH DoDoes

1	InterInv	Verb PersPro Verb

1	PronomVP	Verb
1	PronomVP	Verb NP
1	PronomVP	Verb Location
1	PronomVP	Verb PersPro Verb


# Either/Neither
1	S1	either NP VP or NP VP .
1	S1	neither NP nor NP will speak of it .




# A general mine
1	S1	NP Verb NP .

1	S1	NP Modal Verb ModalVP .
1	ModalVP	Verb
1	ModalVP	Verb Prep NP

1	S1	NP Verb Verb NP .


1	NP	Nbar
20	NP	Det Nbar
10	NP	ProperGroup
1	NP	NP NP
1	NP	Prep NP	

8	ProperGroup	Proper
1	ProperGroup	Det Proper

5	Nbar	Noun
1	Nbar	Adj Noun

